title: agatha chrisi-Miss Marples Final Cases
description:
Published posthumously from middle of Marple's career. UK 8, US 9.
1 Sanctuary - Vicar's wife Bunch hears dying words in church.
2 Strange Jest - Uncle Mathew hides gammon recipe and love letters
3 Tape-Measure - Miss Politt waits with Mrs Spenlow's new dress
4 Caretaker - Dr Haydock prescribes tale: crazy Murgatroyd threatens rich Louise newly wed to troublesome Harry
5 Perfect Maid - Paragon cares for invalid Skinner sister, burgles next door flats
6 Miss Marple Tells a Story - Mr Rhodes accuses of stabbing dramatic wife, but chambermaid left by two doors
Two supernatural -
7 Dressmaker's Doll - Dummy moves around shop by itself
8 In a Glass Darkly - Narrator sees vision, scarred man strangles blonde
US 9 Greenshaw's Folly - Owner dies of arrow to throat(less)
